These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, iced-tea, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, hedgehog, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | tea | soy-milk | iced-tea |
| Pet        | chinchilla | hamster   | turtle | hedgehog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, drama, horror
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, japanese, indonesian, dutch
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the indonesian##1
3. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
4. the malaysian is the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the japanese is on the right of the indonesian##1
6. the malaysian is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | adventure  | satire  | horror |
| Nationality   | dutch    | malaysian | indonesian | japanese    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, spinach, artichoke, garlic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, horror, satire, mystery
1. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person eating artichoke is in an even position##4
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | garlic | artichoke | spinach    | apricot      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire        | mystery     | drama | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, traveling, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, trance, punk, hip-hop
1. the person who's hobby is singing is between the fan of electronic and the fan of hip-hop##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | card-games | singing | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | electronic   | trance    | hip-hop  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, soul, disco, house
There are 4 different nationalities: british, malaysian, polish, german
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the german##1
2. the malaysian is the fan of house##1
3. the polish is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
5. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
6. the british is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | dubstep    | disco   | house       |
| Nationality   | british | german | polish | malaysian |

