3. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
4. the dutch is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the argentine is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | superhero | spy | fantasy |
| Nationality   | canadian | mexican     | dutch  | argentine  |

