.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, animation, horror, disaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, trike, helicopter, train
1. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person driving the train is the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | disaster | horror | animation    |
| Transport     | train | helicopter  | van     | trike |

