.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, firefighter, photographer, electrician
4 different pets are kept: horse, lizard, ferret, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
2. the electrician is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the electrician##3
4. the electrician is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
5. the engineer is between the electrician and the firefighter##2
6. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the lizard is between the engineer and the owner of the ferret##2
8. the engineer is on the left or right of the firefighter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | firefighter | engineer      | electrician | photographer |
| Pet   | horse  | dog | lizard    | ferret            |

