4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, goat, fish
1. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
2. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the snake and the person eating lime##2
4. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating lime is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | grapefruit | corn   | lettuce | lime |
| Pet    | fish     | snake | hedgehog     | goat  |

