.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, tea, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, classical, country, indie
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the fan of indie is between the fan of reggae and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up       | tea   | hot-chocolate | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | country | classical | indie        | reggae    |

