.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, sprite, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, rowing, cricket, basketball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up   | lemonade   | soy-milk      | sprite      |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | basketball | baseball |

