.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, cauliflower, tomato, asparagus
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, punk, metal
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
3. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
4. the person eating kiwi is on the far right##1
5. the person eating tomato is between the fan of reggae and the fan of punk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | asparagus | cauliflower  | tomato  | kiwi |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | punk | dubstep | reggae   |

