.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, writing, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, badminton, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | dancing | card-games         | hiking   | writing |
| Sport   | badminton    | cricket | tennis | biathlon   |

