.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, sudoku, hiking, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, swimming, climbing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | sudoku | video-games | hiking    | fishing |
| Sport   | cycling   | climbing  | snowboarding | swimming     |

