.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, card-games, puzzles, photography
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, thai, british, spanish
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
3. the thai is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the british is on the left or right of the thai##3
5. the thai is between the spanish and the british##2
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | photography   | puzzles | baking | card-games    |
| Nationality   | british | thai  | spanish     | dutch |

