.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, hot-chocolate, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: plum, radish, carrot, orange
1. the person eating radish is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating orange##1
5. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
7. the person eating plum is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | sprite    | hot-chocolate       | coffee |
| Food       | radish  | carrot | orange | plum  |

