.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, french, russian, chinese
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, skateboard, boat
1. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the russian##1
5. the german is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | french | russian | german  | chinese |
| Transport     | helicopter      | skateboard       | scooter | boat     |

