.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, journalist, project-manager, dancer
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, taxi, scooter, bike
1. the journalist is in an even position##4
2. the journalist is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
3. the person driving the taxi is between the teacher and the person driving the motorbike##2
4. the journalist is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the dancer##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | teacher | project-manager   | dancer | journalist |
| Transport   | bike          | taxi | motorbike         | scooter  |

 